Halu my bby!! Almost one week ka ng nasa JBL and HUHUHU I miss our cuddle times very very much! Altho nagagawa parin naman naten kahit konti lang kase nga halos araw araw ka nasa amin pero iba parin yung halos whole day tayo magkasama HUHUHU Buti nalang keri parin pag weekends!!

I love you so much my bby! You opened up to me a few days ago regarding your anxiety sa work and I just want you to know that I support you always! And also that I really do believe na it'll work out well for you! I hope na by the time na you're reading this, settled ka na sa work mo! I know you're a really kind and good and sociable person (ket na sinasabi mo na masama ugali mo), and I really do think that you won't find any problems finding friends in your workplace!! Bbycakes ko yan!! MMWAAA
